<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج د ل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١١٣٠ - ج د ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>جدَّلَ يُجدِّل، تجديلاً، فهو مُجدِّل، والمفعول مُجدَّل<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• جدَّلت شَعْرَها:</span> ضفَّرته.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• جدَّل الرَّجلُ خصمَه:</span> صَرعه <span class="c1">"تركَ خصمَه صريعًا مُجَدَّلاً"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>